quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  54,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  54,1,qayamat qareeb aa pohanchi aur chaand shaqq hogaya
  54,2,aur agar ( kafir ) koi nishani dekhte hain to munh phair letay hain aur kehte hain ke yeh aik hamesha ka jaadoo hai
  54,3,aur unhon ne jhtlaya aur apni khawahishon ki pairwi ki aur har kaam ka waqt muqarrar hai
  54,4,aur un ko aisay halaat ( sabqeen ) poanch chuke hain jin mein Ibrat hai
  54,5,aur kaamil danai ( ki kitaab bhi ) lekin darana un ko kuch faida nahi deta
  54,6,to tum bhi un ki kuch parwa nah karo. jis din bulanay wala un ko aik nakhush cheez ki taraf bulaye ga
  54,7,to ankhen neechi kiye hue qabron se nikal parrin ge goya bhikri hui tiddiyan
  54,8,is bulanay walay ki taraf dorrtay jatay hon ge. kafir kahin ge yeh din bara sakht hai
  54,9,un se pehlay Nooh ki qoum ne bhi takzieeb ki thi to unhon ne hamaray bande ko jhtlaya aur kaha ke deewana hai aur inhen danta bhi
  54,10,to unhon ne apne perwar-digaar se dua ki ke ( baar ilhaa ) mein ( un ke muqablay mein ) kamzor hon to ( un se ) badla le
  54,11,pas hum ne zor ke meen se aasman ke dhanay khol diye
  54,12,aur zameen mein chashmay jari kardiye to pani aik kaam ke liye jo muqaddar hochuka tha jama hogaya
  54,13,aur hum ne Nooh ko aik kashti par jo takhton aur mekhon se tayyar ki gayi thi sawaar karliya
  54,14,woh hamari aankhon ke samnay chalti thi. ( yeh sab kuch ) is shakhs ke intiqam ke liye (kiya gaya ) jis ko kafir mantay nah they
  54,15,aur hum ne is ko aik Ibrat bana chorra to koi hai ke soochey samjhay ?
  54,16,so ( dekh lau ke ) mera azaab aur darana kaisa howa ?
  54,17,aur hum ne quran ko samajhney ke liye aasaan kardiya hai to koi hai ke soochey samjhay ?
  54,18,Aad ne bhi takzieeb ki thi so ( dekh lau ke ) mera azaab aur darana kaisa howa
  54,19,hum ne un par sakht manhoos din mein aandhi chalaye
  54,20,woh logon ko ( is terhan )utharay daalti thi goya akhrhi hui khajoron ke tanay hain
  54,21,so ( dekh lau ke ) mera azaab aur darana kaisa howa
  54,22,aur hum ne quran ko samajhney ke liye aasaan kardiya hai to koi hai ke soochey samjhay ?
  54,23,smod ne bhi hadaayat karne walon ko jhtlaya
  54,24,aur kaha ke bhala aik aadmi jo hum hi mein se hai hum is ki pairwi karen? yun ho to hum gumraahi aur deewangi mein par gay
  54,25,kiya hum sab mein se isi par wahi nazil hui hai? ( nahi ) balkay yeh jhoota khud pasand hai
  54,26,un ko kal hi maloom hojaye ga ke kon jhoota khud pasand hai
  54,27,( ae Saleh ) hum un ki azmaish ke liye oontni bhejnay walay hain to tum un ko dekhte raho aur sabr karo
  54,28,aur un ko aagah kardo ke un mein pani ki baari muqarrar kar di gayi hai. har ( baari walay ko apni ) baari par aana chahiye
  54,29,to un logon ne apne Rafeeq ko bulaya aur is ne ( oontni ko pakar kar is ki ) koncheen kaat dalain
  54,30,so ( dekh lau ke ) mera azaab aur darana kaisa howa
  54,31,hum ne un par ( azaab ke liye ) aik cheekh bhaije to woh aisay hogaye jaisay baar walay ki sookhi aur tooti hui baar
  54,32,aur hum ne quran ko samajhney ke liye aasaan kardiya hai to koi hai ke soochey samjhay ?
  54,33,Loot ki qoum ne bhi dar sunanay walon ko jhtlaya tha
  54,34,to hum ne un par kanker bhari howa chalaye magar Loot ke ghar walay ke hum ne un ko pichli raat hi se bacha liya
  54,35,apne fazl se. shukar karne walon ko hum aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  54,36,aur loot ne un ko hamari pakar se daraya bhi tha magar unhon ne darane mein shakkiya
  54,37,aur un se un ke mehmanon ko le lena chaha to hum ne un ki ankhen mita den so ( ab ) mere azaab aur darane ke mazay chako
  54,38,aur un par subah saweray hi atal azaab aa nazil howa
  54,39,to ab mere azaab aur darane ke mazay chako
  54,40,aur hum ne quran ko samajhney ke liye aasaan kardiya hai to koi hai ke soochey samjhay ?
  54,41,aur qoum firaon ke paas bhi dar sunanay walay aeye
  54,42,unhon ne hamari tamam nshanyon ko jhtlaya to hum ne un ko is terhan pakar liya jis terhan aik quwwat aur ghalib shakhs pakar laita hai
  54,43,( ae ahal arab )kiya tumahray kafir un logon se behtar hain ya tumahray liye ( pehli ) kitabon mein koi farigh khitti likh di gayi hai
  54,44,kiya yeh log kehte hain ke hamari jamaat barri mazboot hai
  54,45,anqareeb yeh jamaat shikast khaye gi aur yeh log peeth phair kar bhaag jayen ge
  54,46,un ke waday ka waqt to qayamat hai aur qayamat barri sakht aur bohat talkh hai
  54,47,be shak gunehgaar log gumraahi aur deewangi mein ( mubtala ) hain
  54,48,is roz munh ke bil dozakh mein ghsite jayen ge ab aag ka maza chako
  54,49,hum ne har cheez andazah ٴ muqarrar ke sath peda ki hai
  54,50,aur hamara hukum to aankhh ke jhapkane ki terhan aik baat hoti hai
  54,51,aur hum tumahray hum mzhbon ko halaak kar chukay hain to koi hai ke soochey samjhay ?
  54,52,"aur jo kuch unhon nekiya, ( un ke ) aamaal naamon mein ( mndrj ) hai"
  54,53,( yani ) har chhota aur bara kaam likh diya gaya hai
  54,54,jo parhaizgaar hain woh baghoon aur nﮦron mein hon ge
  54,55,( yani ) pak maqam mein har terhan ki qudrat rakhnay walay badshah ki bargaah mein
